	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />- I'd like to request to someone else with a devkit to run the following test in the NES.
<br />
<br />1. boot up (around 1 second)
<br />2. SEI to prevent IRQs to trip
<br />3. select apu mode 0 (4 steps) by writting to 4017h.
<br />4. wait a few frames (around 1 second too)
<br />5. select apu mode 1 (5 steps) by writting to 4017h.
<br />6. wait a few frames (around 1 second too)
<br />7. CLI to allow IRQs to trip
<br />8. check if an IRQ was triggered and print the result.
<br />
<br />- Please, let me know the results. I would thank you a lot. ^_^;;

		

		</td>
	</tr>
